{
  "video_id": "y52LeaK6tHA",
  "title": "President Obama Addresses the Nation on Syria",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13000.0,
      "end_time": 15200.0,
      "text": "The President: My fellow Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15200.0,
      "end_time": 17934.0,
      "text": "tonight I want to talk to you about Syria --"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17934.0,
      "end_time": 21934.0,
      "text": "why it matters, and where we go from here."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21934.0,
      "end_time": 23300.0,
      "text": "Over the past two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23300.0,
      "end_time": 26000.0,
      "text": "what began as a series of peaceful protests"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26000.0,
      "end_time": 28834.0,
      "text": "against the repressive regime of Bashar al-Assad"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28834.0,
      "end_time": 30734.0,
      "text": "has turned into a brutal civil war."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30734.0,
      "end_time": 34934.0,
      "text": "Over 100,000 people have been killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34934.0,
      "end_time": 37467.0,
      "text": "Millions have fled the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37467.0,
      "end_time": 39467.0,
      "text": "In that time, America has worked with allies"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39467.0,
      "end_time": 41567.0,
      "text": "to provide humanitarian support,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41567.0,
      "end_time": 43934.0,
      "text": "to help the moderate opposition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43934.0,
      "end_time": 45500.0,
      "text": "and to shape a political settlement."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45500.0,
      "end_time": 50000.0,
      "text": "But I have resisted calls for military action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50000.0,
      "end_time": 51333.0,
      "text": "because we cannot resolve"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51333.0,
      "end_time": 54734.0,
      "text": "someone else's civil war through force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54734.0,
      "end_time": 59800.0,
      "text": "particularly after a decade of war in Iraq and Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59800.0,
      "end_time": 64266.0,
      "text": "The situation profoundly changed, though, on August 21st,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64266.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68600.0,
      "text": "when Assad's government gassed to death over a thousand people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68600.0,
      "end_time": 71533.0,
      "text": "including hundreds of children."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71533.0,
      "end_time": 76700.0,
      "text": "The images from this massacre are sickening: Men, women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 76700.0,
      "end_time": 80667.0,
      "text": "children lying in rows, killed by poison gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 80667.0,
      "end_time": 84834.0,
      "text": "Others foaming at the mouth, gasping for breath."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84834.0,
      "end_time": 87300.0,
      "text": "A father clutching his dead children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87300.0,
      "end_time": 89266.0,
      "text": "imploring them to get up and walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89266.0,
      "end_time": 94967.0,
      "text": "On that terrible night, the world saw in gruesome detail"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94967.0,
      "end_time": 97633.0,
      "text": "the terrible nature of chemical weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97633.0,
      "end_time": 100233.0,
      "text": "and why the overwhelming majority of humanity"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100233.0,
      "end_time": 102967.0,
      "text": "has declared them off-limits --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102967.0,
      "end_time": 104934.0,
      "text": "a crime against humanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104934.0,
      "end_time": 109000.0,
      "text": "and a violation of the laws of war."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 109000.0,
      "end_time": 111467.0,
      "text": "This was not always the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111467.0,
      "end_time": 114900.0,
      "text": "In World War I, American GIs were among the many thousands"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114900.0,
      "end_time": 118567.0,
      "text": "killed by deadly gas in the trenches of Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118567.0,
      "end_time": 121266.0,
      "text": "In World War II, the Nazis used gas"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121266.0,
      "end_time": 124834.0,
      "text": "to inflict the horror of the Holocaust."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124834.0,
      "end_time": 127900.0,
      "text": "Because these weapons can kill on a mass scale,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127900.0,
      "end_time": 130867.0,
      "text": "with no distinction between soldier and infant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130866.99999999999,
      "end_time": 135333.0,
      "text": "the civilized world has spent a century working to ban them."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 135333.0,
      "end_time": 138700.0,
      "text": "And in 1997, the United States Senate"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138700.0,
      "end_time": 141867.0,
      "text": "overwhelmingly approved an international agreement"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141867.0,
      "end_time": 144200.0,
      "text": "prohibiting the use of chemical weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 146467.0,
      "text": "now joined by 189 governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146467.0,
      "end_time": 151500.0,
      "text": "that represent 98 percent of humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151500.0,
      "end_time": 155800.0,
      "text": "On August 21st, these basic rules were violated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 155800.0,
      "end_time": 159133.0,
      "text": "along with our sense of common humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 159133.0,
      "end_time": 163867.0,
      "text": "No one disputes that chemical weapons were used in Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163867.0,
      "end_time": 167367.0,
      "text": "The world saw thousands of videos, cell phone pictures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 167367.0,
      "end_time": 169400.0,
      "text": "and social media accounts from the attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169400.0,
      "end_time": 172867.0,
      "text": "and humanitarian organizations told stories of hospitals"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172867.0,
      "end_time": 177900.0,
      "text": "packed with people who had symptoms of poison gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177900.0,
      "end_time": 182533.0,
      "text": "Moreover, we know the Assad regime was responsible."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182533.0,
      "end_time": 184633.0,
      "text": "In the days leading up to August 21st,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 184633.0,
      "end_time": 188000.0,
      "text": "we know that Assad's chemical weapons personnel prepared"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188000.0,
      "end_time": 192400.0,
      "text": "for an attack near an area where they mix sarin gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192400.0,
      "end_time": 195633.0,
      "text": "They distributed gasmasks to their troops."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 195633.0,
      "end_time": 198166.0,
      "text": "Then they fired rockets from a regime-controlled area"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 198166.0,
      "end_time": 200834.0,
      "text": "into 11 neighborhoods that the regime"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200834.0,
      "end_time": 204533.0,
      "text": "has been trying to wipe clear of opposition forces."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204533.0,
      "end_time": 208033.0,
      "text": "Shortly after those rockets landed, the gas spread,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 208033.0,
      "end_time": 212200.0,
      "text": "and hospitals filled with the dying and the wounded."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 212200.0,
      "end_time": 214900.0,
      "text": "We know senior figures in Assad's military machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 214900.0,
      "end_time": 217333.0,
      "text": "reviewed the results of the attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217333.0,
      "end_time": 219233.0,
      "text": "and the regime increased their shelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219233.0,
      "end_time": 223367.0,
      "text": "of the same neighborhoods in the days that followed."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223367.0,
      "end_time": 226266.0,
      "text": "We've also studied samples of blood and hair from people"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226266.0,
      "end_time": 232033.0,
      "text": "at the site that tested positive for sarin."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 232033.0,
      "end_time": 234900.0,
      "text": "When dictators commit atrocities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 234900.0,
      "end_time": 238033.0,
      "text": "they depend upon the world to look the other way"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 238033.0,
      "end_time": 241800.0,
      "text": "until those horrifying pictures fade from memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 241800.0,
      "end_time": 244166.0,
      "text": "But these things happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 244166.0,
      "end_time": 245934.0,
      "text": "The facts cannot be denied."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245934.0,
      "end_time": 250400.0,
      "text": "The question now is what the United States of America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 250400.0,
      "end_time": 255100.0,
      "text": "and the international community, is prepared to do about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255100.0,
      "end_time": 257533.0,
      "text": "Because what happened to those people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 257533.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259066.00000000003,
      "text": "to those children --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 259065.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262433.0,
      "text": "is not only a violation of international law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 262433.0,
      "end_time": 266367.0,
      "text": "it's also a danger to our security."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 266367.0,
      "end_time": 268700.0,
      "text": "Let me explain why."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 268700.0,
      "end_time": 272033.0,
      "text": "If we fail to act, the Assad regime will see no reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272033.0,
      "end_time": 274867.0,
      "text": "to stop using chemical weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 274867.0,
      "end_time": 277600.0,
      "text": "As the ban against these weapons erodes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 277600.0,
      "end_time": 279734.0,
      "text": "other tyrants will have no reason to think twice"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 279734.0,
      "end_time": 284133.0,
      "text": "about acquiring poison gas, and using them."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284133.0,
      "end_time": 286567.0,
      "text": "Over time, our troops would again face the prospect"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 286567.0,
      "end_time": 289266.0,
      "text": "of chemical warfare on the battlefield."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 289266.0,
      "end_time": 291667.0,
      "text": "And it could be easier for terrorist organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 291667.0,
      "end_time": 293133.0,
      "text": "to obtain these weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293133.0,
      "end_time": 296567.0,
      "text": "and to use them to attack civilians."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 296567.0,
      "end_time": 298734.0,
      "text": "If fighting spills beyond Syria's borders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 298734.0,
      "end_time": 301266.0,
      "text": "these weapons could threaten allies like Turkey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 301266.0,
      "end_time": 303867.0,
      "text": "Jordan, and Israel."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 303867.0,
      "end_time": 307533.0,
      "text": "And a failure to stand against the use of chemical weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 307533.0,
      "end_time": 308600.0,
      "text": "would weaken prohibitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 308600.0,
      "end_time": 311533.0,
      "text": "against other weapons of mass destruction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 311533.0,
      "end_time": 313967.0,
      "text": "and embolden Assad's ally, Iran --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 313967.0,
      "end_time": 316300.0,
      "text": "which must decide whether to ignore international law"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 316300.0,
      "end_time": 322333.0,
      "text": "by building a nuclear weapon, or to take a more peaceful path."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 322333.0,
      "end_time": 325567.0,
      "text": "This is not a world we should accept."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 325567.0,
      "end_time": 326800.0,
      "text": "This is what's at stake."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 326800.0,
      "end_time": 330767.0,
      "text": "And that is why, after careful deliberation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 330767.0,
      "end_time": 334233.0,
      "text": "I determined that it is in the national security interests"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 334233.0,
      "end_time": 338133.0,
      "text": "of the United States to respond to the Assad regime's use"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 338133.0,
      "end_time": 342934.0,
      "text": "of chemical weapons through a targeted military strike."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 342934.0,
      "end_time": 345734.0,
      "text": "The purpose of this strike would be to deter Assad from using"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 345734.0,
      "end_time": 349934.0,
      "text": "chemical weapons, to degrade his regime's ability to use them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 349934.0,
      "end_time": 351667.0,
      "text": "and to make clear to the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 351667.0,
      "end_time": 356233.0,
      "text": "that we will not tolerate their use."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 356233.0,
      "end_time": 358100.0,
      "text": "That's my judgment as Commander-in-Chief."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358100.0,
      "end_time": 361033.0,
      "text": "But I'm also the President of the world's"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 361033.0,
      "end_time": 363600.0,
      "text": "oldest constitutional democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 363600.0,
      "end_time": 365500.0,
      "text": "So even though I possess the authority"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 365500.0,
      "end_time": 367567.0,
      "text": "to order military strikes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 367567.0,
      "end_time": 369233.0,
      "text": "I believed it was right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 369233.0,
      "end_time": 372700.0,
      "text": "in the absence of a direct or imminent threat to our security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 372700.0,
      "end_time": 375800.0,
      "text": "to take this debate to Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 375800.0,
      "end_time": 378500.0,
      "text": "I believe our democracy is stronger when the President acts"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 378500.0,
      "end_time": 380734.0,
      "text": "with the support of Congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 380734.0,
      "end_time": 383767.0,
      "text": "And I believe that America acts more effectively abroad"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 383767.0,
      "end_time": 385133.0,
      "text": "when we stand together."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385133.0,
      "end_time": 389166.0,
      "text": "This is especially true after a decade that put more and more"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 389166.0,
      "end_time": 391767.0,
      "text": "war-making power in the hands of the President,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 391767.0,
      "end_time": 394800.0,
      "text": "and more and more burdens on the shoulders of our troops,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 394800.0,
      "end_time": 396800.0,
      "text": "while sidelining the people's representatives"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396800.0,
      "end_time": 402200.0,
      "text": "from the critical decisions about when we use force."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 402200.0,
      "end_time": 405100.0,
      "text": "Now, I know that after the terrible toll"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 405100.0,
      "end_time": 409433.0,
      "text": "of Iraq and Afghanistan, the idea of any military action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 409433.0,
      "end_time": 414333.0,
      "text": "no matter how limited, is not going to be popular."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 414333.0,
      "end_time": 416433.0,
      "text": "After all, I've spent four and a half years"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 416433.0,
      "end_time": 419734.0,
      "text": "working to end wars, not to start them."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 419734.0,
      "end_time": 421934.0,
      "text": "Our troops are out of Iraq."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 421934.0,
      "end_time": 424867.0,
      "text": "Our troops are coming home from Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424867.0,
      "end_time": 427834.0,
      "text": "And I know Americans want all of us in Washington --"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 427834.0,
      "end_time": 429333.0,
      "text": "especially me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429333.0,
      "end_time": 430800.0,
      "text": "to concentrate on the task"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 430800.0,
      "end_time": 433467.0,
      "text": "of building our nation here at home:"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 433467.0,
      "end_time": 437266.0,
      "text": "putting people back to work, educating our kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 437266.0,
      "end_time": 440233.0,
      "text": "growing our middle class."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 440233.0,
      "end_time": 443734.0,
      "text": "It's no wonder, then, that you're asking hard questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443734.0,
      "end_time": 445900.0,
      "text": "So let me answer some of the most important questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 445900.0,
      "end_time": 447700.0,
      "text": "that I've heard from members of Congress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 447700.0,
      "end_time": 452133.0,
      "text": "and that I've read in letters that you've sent to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 452133.0,
      "end_time": 454967.0,
      "text": "First, many of you have asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 454967.0,
      "end_time": 459667.0,
      "text": "won't this put us on a slippery slope to another war?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459667.0,
      "end_time": 462100.0,
      "text": "One man wrote to me that we are \"still recovering"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 462100.0,
      "end_time": 464667.0,
      "text": "from our involvement in Iraq.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 464667.0,
      "end_time": 466734.0,
      "text": "A veteran put it more bluntly:"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 466734.0,
      "end_time": 471133.0,
      "text": "\"This nation is sick and tired of war.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 471133.0,
      "end_time": 473333.0,
      "text": "My answer is simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 473333.0,
      "end_time": 477800.0,
      "text": "I will not put American boots on the ground in Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 477800.0,
      "end_time": 483200.0,
      "text": "I will not pursue an open-ended action like Iraq or Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 483200.0,
      "end_time": 485567.0,
      "text": "I will not pursue a prolonged air campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 485567.0,
      "end_time": 488100.0,
      "text": "like Libya or Kosovo."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 488100.0,
      "end_time": 492133.0,
      "text": "This would be a targeted strike to achieve a clear objective:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 492133.0,
      "end_time": 494600.0,
      "text": "deterring the use of chemical weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 494600.0,
      "end_time": 498800.0,
      "text": "and degrading Assad's capabilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 498800.0,
      "end_time": 501166.0,
      "text": "Others have asked whether it's worth acting"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 501166.0,
      "end_time": 503633.0,
      "text": "if we don't take out Assad."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 503633.0,
      "end_time": 505333.0,
      "text": "As some members of Congress have said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 505333.0,
      "end_time": 511233.0,
      "text": "there's no point in simply doing a \"pinprick\" strike in Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511233.0,
      "end_time": 513367.0,
      "text": "Let me make something clear:"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513366.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518065.99999999994,
      "text": "The United States military doesn't do pinpricks."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 518066.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521066.00000000006,
      "text": "Even a limited strike will send a message to Assad"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 521066.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524767.0,
      "text": "that no other nation can deliver."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 524767.0,
      "end_time": 527767.0,
      "text": "I don't think we should remove another dictator with force --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 527767.0,
      "end_time": 530567.0,
      "text": "we learned from Iraq that doing so makes us responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 530567.0,
      "end_time": 532633.0,
      "text": "for all that comes next."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 532633.0,
      "end_time": 536800.0,
      "text": "But a targeted strike can make Assad, or any other dictator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 536800.0,
      "end_time": 541934.0,
      "text": "think twice before using chemical weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 541934.0,
      "end_time": 546266.0,
      "text": "Other questions involve the dangers of retaliation."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 546266.0,
      "end_time": 549400.0,
      "text": "We don't dismiss any threats, but the Assad regime does not"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 549400.0,
      "end_time": 552967.0,
      "text": "have the ability to seriously threaten our military."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 552967.0,
      "end_time": 556667.0,
      "text": "Any other retaliation they might seek is in line with threats"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 556667.0,
      "end_time": 560033.0,
      "text": "that we face every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 560033.0,
      "end_time": 563367.0,
      "text": "Neither Assad nor his allies have any interest in escalation"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 563367.0,
      "end_time": 564967.0,
      "text": "that would lead to his demise."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 564967.0,
      "end_time": 570233.0,
      "text": "And our ally, Israel, can defend itself with overwhelming force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 570233.0,
      "end_time": 572400.0,
      "text": "as well as the unshakable support"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 572400.0,
      "end_time": 576767.0,
      "text": "of the United States of America."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 576767.0,
      "end_time": 580133.0,
      "text": "Many of you have asked a broader question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 580133.0,
      "end_time": 582133.0,
      "text": "Why should we get involved at all"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 582133.0,
      "end_time": 584367.0,
      "text": "in a place that's so complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 584367.0,
      "end_time": 586867.0,
      "text": "and where -- as one person wrote to me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 586867.0,
      "end_time": 592200.0,
      "text": "\"those who come after Assad may be enemies of human rights?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 592200.0,
      "end_time": 596700.0,
      "text": "It's true that some of Assad's opponents are extremists."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 596700.0,
      "end_time": 600767.0,
      "text": "But al Qaeda will only draw strength in a more chaotic Syria"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 600767.0,
      "end_time": 604200.0,
      "text": "if people there see the world doing nothing to prevent"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 604200.0,
      "end_time": 608367.0,
      "text": "innocent civilians from being gassed to death."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 608367.0,
      "end_time": 610166.0,
      "text": "The majority of the Syrian people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 610166.0,
      "end_time": 612667.0,
      "text": "and the Syrian opposition we work with --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 612667.0,
      "end_time": 617200.0,
      "text": "just want to live in peace, with dignity and freedom."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 617200.0,
      "end_time": 619767.0,
      "text": "And the day after any military action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 619767.0,
      "end_time": 623467.0,
      "text": "we would redouble our efforts to achieve a political solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 623467.0,
      "end_time": 625734.0,
      "text": "that strengthens those who reject the forces"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 625734.0,
      "end_time": 630767.0,
      "text": "of tyranny and extremism."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 630767.0,
      "end_time": 633166.0,
      "text": "Finally, many of you have asked:"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 633166.0,
      "end_time": 635467.0,
      "text": "Why not leave this to other countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 635467.0,
      "end_time": 639767.0,
      "text": "or seek solutions short of force?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 639767.0,
      "end_time": 641433.0,
      "text": "As several people wrote to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 641433.0,
      "end_time": 644567.0,
      "text": "\"We should not be the world's policeman.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 644567.0,
      "end_time": 648400.0,
      "text": "I agree, and I have a deeply held preference"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 648400.0,
      "end_time": 651233.0,
      "text": "for peaceful solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 651233.0,
      "end_time": 652433.0,
      "text": "Over the last two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 652433.0,
      "end_time": 655967.0,
      "text": "my administration has tried diplomacy and sanctions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 655967.0,
      "end_time": 658700.0,
      "text": "warnings and negotiations --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 658700.0,
      "end_time": 663867.0,
      "text": "but chemical weapons were still used by the Assad regime."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 663867.0,
      "end_time": 665867.0,
      "text": "However, over the last few days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 665867.0,
      "end_time": 669233.0,
      "text": "we've seen some encouraging signs."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 669233.0,
      "end_time": 671734.0,
      "text": "In part because of the credible threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 671734.0,
      "end_time": 673633.0,
      "text": "of U.S. military action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 673633.0,
      "end_time": 677233.0,
      "text": "as well as constructive talks that I had with President Putin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 677233.0,
      "end_time": 679300.0,
      "text": "the Russian government has indicated a willingness"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 679300.0,
      "end_time": 682900.0,
      "text": "to join with the international community in pushing Assad"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 682900.0,
      "end_time": 686266.0,
      "text": "to give up his chemical weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 686266.0,
      "end_time": 687867.0,
      "text": "The Assad regime has now admitted"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 687867.0,
      "end_time": 689533.0,
      "text": "that it has these weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 689533.0,
      "end_time": 692400.0,
      "text": "and even said they'd join the Chemical Weapons Convention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 692400.0,
      "end_time": 695400.0,
      "text": "which prohibits their use."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 695400.0,
      "end_time": 698266.0,
      "text": "It's too early to tell whether this offer will succeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 698266.0,
      "end_time": 701800.0,
      "text": "and any agreement must verify that the Assad regime"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 701800.0,
      "end_time": 704166.0,
      "text": "keeps its commitments."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 704166.0,
      "end_time": 707166.0,
      "text": "But this initiative has the potential to remove the threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 707166.0,
      "end_time": 710300.0,
      "text": "of chemical weapons without the use of force,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 710300.0,
      "end_time": 715033.0,
      "text": "particularly because Russia is one of Assad's strongest allies."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 715033.0,
      "end_time": 717633.0,
      "text": "I have, therefore, asked the leaders of Congress"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 717633.0,
      "end_time": 720600.0,
      "text": "to postpone a vote to authorize the use of force"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 720600.0,
      "end_time": 723934.0,
      "text": "while we pursue this diplomatic path."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 723934.0,
      "end_time": 725667.0,
      "text": "I'm sending Secretary of State John Kerry"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 725667.0,
      "end_time": 728300.0,
      "text": "to meet his Russian counterpart on Thursday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 728300.0,
      "end_time": 729834.0,
      "text": "and I will continue my own discussions"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 729834.0,
      "end_time": 732033.0,
      "text": "with President Putin."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 732033.0,
      "end_time": 734800.0,
      "text": "I've spoken to the leaders of two of our closest allies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 734800.0,
      "end_time": 737767.0,
      "text": "France and the United Kingdom, and we will work together"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 737767.0,
      "end_time": 740900.0,
      "text": "in consultation with Russia and China to put forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 740900.0,
      "end_time": 743100.0,
      "text": "a resolution at the U.N. Security Council"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 743100.0,
      "end_time": 746166.0,
      "text": "requiring Assad to give up his chemical weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 746166.0,
      "end_time": 751233.0,
      "text": "and to ultimately destroy them under international control."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 751233.0,
      "end_time": 753233.0,
      "text": "We'll also give U.N. inspectors the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 753233.0,
      "end_time": 757133.0,
      "text": "to report their findings about what happened on August 21st."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 757133.0,
      "end_time": 759700.0,
      "text": "And we will continue to rally support from allies"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 759700.0,
      "end_time": 761633.0,
      "text": "from Europe to the Americas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 761633.0,
      "end_time": 763367.0,
      "text": "from Asia to the Middle East --"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 763367.0,
      "end_time": 766967.0,
      "text": "who agree on the need for action."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 766967.0,
      "end_time": 769066.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, I've ordered our military"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 769066.0,
      "end_time": 771333.0,
      "text": "to maintain their current posture"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 771333.0,
      "end_time": 773400.0,
      "text": "to keep the pressure on Assad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 773400.0,
      "end_time": 777567.0,
      "text": "and to be in a position to respond if diplomacy fails."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 777567.0,
      "end_time": 778834.0,
      "text": "And tonight, I give thanks again"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 778834.0,
      "end_time": 780400.0,
      "text": "to our military and their families"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 780400.0,
      "end_time": 785467.0,
      "text": "for their incredible strength and sacrifices."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 785467.0,
      "end_time": 788800.0,
      "text": "My fellow Americans, for nearly seven decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 788800.0,
      "end_time": 791967.0,
      "text": "the United States has been the anchor of global security."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 791967.0,
      "end_time": 794567.0,
      "text": "This has meant doing more"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 794567.0,
      "end_time": 797600.0,
      "text": "than forging international agreements --"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 797600.0,
      "end_time": 800967.0,
      "text": "it has meant enforcing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 800967.0,
      "end_time": 804100.0,
      "text": "The burdens of leadership are often heavy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 804100.0,
      "end_time": 806700.0,
      "text": "but the world is a better place because we have borne them."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 806700.0,
      "end_time": 810333.0,
      "text": "And so, to my friends on the right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 810333.0,
      "end_time": 812166.0,
      "text": "I ask you to reconcile your commitment"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 812166.0,
      "end_time": 814633.0,
      "text": "to Ameria's military might"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 814633.0,
      "end_time": 819967.0,
      "text": "with a failure to act when a cause is so plainly just."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 819967.0,
      "end_time": 821834.0,
      "text": "To my friends on the left,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 821834.0,
      "end_time": 823367.0,
      "text": "I ask you to reconcile your belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 823367.0,
      "end_time": 825867.0,
      "text": "in freedom and dignity for all people"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 825867.0,
      "end_time": 828767.0,
      "text": "with those images of children writhing in pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 828767.0,
      "end_time": 833700.0,
      "text": "and going still on a cold hospital floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 833700.0,
      "end_time": 837467.0,
      "text": "For sometimes resolutions and statements of condemnation"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 837467.0,
      "end_time": 841800.0,
      "text": "are simply not enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 841800.0,
      "end_time": 844333.0,
      "text": "Indeed, I'd ask every member of Congress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 844333.0,
      "end_time": 846667.0,
      "text": "and those of you watching at home tonight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 846667.0,
      "end_time": 849667.0,
      "text": "to view those videos of the attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 849667.0,
      "end_time": 852767.0,
      "text": "and then ask: What kind of world will we live in"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 852767.0,
      "end_time": 855667.0,
      "text": "if the United States of America sees a dictator"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 855667.0,
      "end_time": 859800.0,
      "text": "brazenly violate international law with poison gas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 859800.0,
      "end_time": 863800.0,
      "text": "and we choose to look the other way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 863800.0,
      "end_time": 866934.0,
      "text": "Franklin Roosevelt once said, \"Our national determination"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 866934.0,
      "end_time": 871200.0,
      "text": "to keep free of foreign wars and foreign entanglements"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 871200.0,
      "end_time": 874000.0,
      "text": "cannot prevent us from feeling deep concern"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 874000.0,
      "end_time": 875800.0,
      "text": "when ideals and principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 875800.0,
      "end_time": 880233.0,
      "text": "that we have cherished are challenged.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 880233.0,
      "end_time": 882867.0,
      "text": "Our ideals and principles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 882867.0,
      "end_time": 884266.0,
      "text": "as well as our national security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 884266.0,
      "end_time": 888433.0,
      "text": "are at stake in Syria, along with our leadership"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 888433.0,
      "end_time": 892266.0,
      "text": "of a world where we seek to ensure that the worst weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 892266.0,
      "end_time": 895467.0,
      "text": "will never be used."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 895467.0,
      "end_time": 898500.0,
      "text": "America is not the world's policeman."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 898500.0,
      "end_time": 901533.0,
      "text": "Terrible things happen across the globe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 901533.0,
      "end_time": 905633.0,
      "text": "and it is beyond our means to right every wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 905633.0,
      "end_time": 909100.0,
      "text": "But when, with modest effort and risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 909100.0,
      "end_time": 912200.0,
      "text": "we can stop children from being gassed to death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 912200.0,
      "end_time": 914166.0,
      "text": "and thereby make our own children safer"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 914166.0,
      "end_time": 916066.0,
      "text": "over the long run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 916066.0,
      "end_time": 918767.0,
      "text": "I believe we should act."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 918767.0,
      "end_time": 921367.0,
      "text": "That's what makes America different."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 921367.0,
      "end_time": 924467.0,
      "text": "That's what makes us exceptional."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 924467.0,
      "end_time": 927200.0,
      "text": "With humility, but with resolve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 927200.0,
      "end_time": 931000.0,
      "text": "let us never lose sight of that essential truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 931000.0,
      "end_time": 932000.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 932000.0,
      "end_time": 933066.0,
      "text": "God bless you."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 933066.0,
      "end_time": 943066.0,
      "text": "And God bless the United States of America."
    }
  ]
}